    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275012</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>すげー、かっこよすぎ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Amazing! This is the coolest!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;超古代都市トール&lt;White&gt;だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is technology you'd only see
in The &lt;Red&gt;Ancient City of Thor&lt;White&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この街の
マザーコンピューターシステムに
時間転移の機能があるんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Inside this city, there is a Master Computer
System. One of the facilities allows for
space-time travel.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ルー……クルール？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ru...Kuruuru?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ま、百聞は一見にしかず、だ。
行こうぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Explaining it gives me a headache.
You'll see what we mean once
you're there. Let's go, then!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ねぇ、エト。このまま、
戻っちゃってもいいの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Say, Eto. I've been thinking...
Is it okay to return?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275760</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>本当はまだ自分が何者か、
ひっかかってるんじゃない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Isn't there something you want
to wrap up in this era?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276196</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>前に&lt;Dio&gt;が
言ってたでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's like &lt;Dio&gt; said before.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276196</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>別にぼくが妖精でも何でも、
何も変わらないって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whether I'm a fairy or not,
it doesn't change anything.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276276</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなことオレ、
言ったか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I said that? When was that?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276340</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>言ったよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You don't remember?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276592</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;ヴァルハラ町&lt;White&gt;のことが
決着ついたら、エトのこと
調べる、わたし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Once everything in &lt;Red&gt;Valhalla&lt;White&gt; is
settled, I promise I'll help figure
out what you are.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276692</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……あ、いや、
別にそんなの……
……ほんとに？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Th-That's not ne--... W-Would
you really do that for me?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276784</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エトには、
いつも明るくいて
ほしいから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Of course! I want you
to always be happy.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276856</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ありがとう、&lt;Mel&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thanks, &lt;Mel&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276964</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_010_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>っし！　早くこっちのカタつけて、
戻ろうぜ、元の時代に</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>C'mon! Let's take care of this
so we can go back home!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
